Epidemiology
Source of the outbreak(s) or origin of infection: unknown or inconclusive

Control measures
Measures applied: movement control inside the country, surveillance outside infected and/or protection zone, screening, zoning, disinfection, vaccination permitted (if a vaccine exists), no treatment of affected animals
Measures to be applied: No other measures

